## Note about the existing CLAUDE.md

There's an existing `CLAUDE.md` in this repo that just imports `AGENTS.md` (a Next.js-specific note about reading the local docs before writing code). When merging this proposed file, keep the AGENTS.md import — either prepend `@AGENTS.md` at the top of this file, or merge AGENTS.md content directly into the agent-onboarding section.
